sys_hub_action_type_definition.description:
Describes the specified target groups or all of your target groups.

Inputs:

  • Region - Amazon region.
  • Target Group ARN - ARN of target group.

Outputs:

  • Target Groups - Object containing information about the targets.
    • Target Group ARN
    • Health Check Enabled
    • Protocol
    • Port
    • Target Group Name
    • Vpc ID
    • Health Check Interval Seconds
    • Health Check Timeout Seconds
(For information about the errors that are common to all actions, see Common Errors).

To use this action, the corresponding AWS Elastic Load Balancing connection and credential must be created and associated with the AWS Elastic Load Balancing Connection & Credential alias. Learn More
